Test designs for Sayma boards (ddr3, drtio, serwb, jesd204b)

[> Status
---------
- ddr3: 32 bit and 64 bit ddr3 validated @ 1Gbps/pin.
- drtio: MultiGTH validated with 2 lanes @ 3Gbps.
- serwb: validated between AMC (Master) & RTM (Slave) @ 1.25Gbps.
- jesd204b: validated @ 6Gbps (tested up to 10Gbps).
